{"type":null,"faqId":46169,"title":"荣耀7i手机出现自动关机/开不了机情况如何进行恢复？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:0.14583333in;margin-left:0.875in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:0.14583333in;margin-left:0.875in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>一：普通检查：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1、检查手机卡及内存卡（SD卡）的插卡方向是否正确，有时候安装不正常也会导致自动关机。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2、检查手机电量是否有电（通过插上充电看充电界面），电量不足2%会导致自动关机。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3、软件问题导致自动关机，请确认近期是否装了什么不兼容的应用导致手机近期突然异常关机。建议用户恢复出厂设置并升级到最新的软件版本。（恢复出厂设置前请提前备份好关键数据）</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>长按电源键10秒以上进行手机强制重启，如果手机能够正常进入到待机界面，则通过普通升级恢复操作方式进行手机修复。如果仍无法开机/无法重启，则通过强制升级恢复操作方式进行手</span><span class=\"s1\">机修复。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>二. 普通的升级恢复方式</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1）恢复出厂设置</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作步骤，手机设置中，依次点击备份和重置-恢复出厂设置-重置手机，手机重启后会完成恢复出厂设置，然后自动重启正常使用。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2）在线升级</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>操作步骤（要保证手机连上WLAN，可以上网），设置-系统更新-检查更新-选中新版本-选择下载并安装启动升级。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>三、强制恢复方式</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>由于手机不能开机，以下恢复方法会导致您数据丢失，请平时做好关键数据的备份。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1、下载软件版本</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>请提前到emui网站（http://www.emui.com/plugin.php?id=hwdownload）上下载对应手机的软件版本。下面以P7联通为例查找版本。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170788\" style=\"width:5.759722in;height:3.0722222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170789\" style=\"width:5.3951387in;height:2.3854167in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170790\" style=\"width:5.3013887in;height:2.895139in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":141,"faqType":"备份恢复与升级","useful":0,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1949","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Backup-Restore-Update","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444376113000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":406,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":15,"times":5,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"root,恢复,自动重启","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}